data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom home in a desirable neighborhood! This lovely property boasts a brand new fence for added privacy and security. Inside, you'll find a cozy living room with a fireplace, perfect for those chilly nights. The home features energy-efficient HP mini splits, ensuring year-round comfort. The newer roof provides peace of mind for the future. Covered parking ensures your vehicle stays protected. Whether you're a first-time buyer or looking to downsize, this home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours! Schedule a viewing today!
